{"tid":1744672,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"人民日報指香港享有比歷史上任何時候都廣泛的民主","createTime":"2019-11-22T00:49:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T06:32:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"913c734c13a748100d94de7725506a239303926f","tid":1744672,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:49:18.000Z","msg":"人民日報海外版發表專欄文章，批評美國國會不顧中國政府多次強烈反對，通過《香港人權與民主法案》，如果美方一意孤行，中方必將採取有力措施予以反制，一切後果由美方完全承擔。<br />\n<br />\n文章說，法案內容顛倒黑白、混淆視聽，絲毫站不住腳，批評美國政客無資格對一個自由度及法治排名都高於自己的別國地區，指手畫腳，強調香港回歸以來，一國兩制實踐取得舉世公認的成功，香港作為國際金融、航運、貿易中心的地位不斷鞏固，香港同胞享有比歷史上任何時候都廣泛的民主權利與自由。<br />\n<br />\n文章再次要求美方立即停止插手香港事務、干涉中國內政，認清大勢、懸崖勒馬。<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1493781_1_20191122054055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1493781_1_20191122054055.jpg&h=22cdc556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493781-20191122.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493781-20191122.htm&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt802FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=1a3397ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493781-20191122.htm&h=a651260d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493781-20191122.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n每日一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce958945bc085c188afbe7864339156a2ff157f","tid":1744672,"uid":286412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:49:41.000Z","msg":"18-11-2019 (原片）香港警察踩示威者頭部<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737274</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你好我係拍片嘅本人，有冇人知道個手足點樣？可以幫手retweet 比多啲人睇到,想推到出國際記者報道，謝謝 Twitter link <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Ng1